      "role": "user",
      "content": "thx. could u go into a bit more detail on that last point though? u mentioned dependency on govt support. specifically for groups coming from developing nations or regions with less stability, what are the common arguments people use to claim they're a bigger drain compared to, say, high-skilled migrants from western countries?",
